data.description: Enjoy this private and well maintained home with seasonal mountain views.  Minutes to 29, for an easy commute to Greene, Cville or Culpeper.  Home has been updated to include new appliances, backsplash, cabinets w/under lights, and flooring in kitchen.  New 20 x 20 composite deck off dining room with a patio off basement door.  Sit by the firepit for a night cap or watch wildlife.  Recess lighting was added to main level.  New front door and roof was replaced in Summer of 2023. Upstairs has new floors, bathroom cabinet, fixtures and flooring throughout.
